14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Department of
16 Mental Health and Substance Abuse Services from any monies not
17 otherwise appropriated from the Statewide Recovery Fund of the State
18 Treasury created in Section 255 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma
19 Statutes, the sum of Seven Million Nine Hundred Twenty-nine Thousand
20 Five Hundred Ninety-six Dollars and forty-five cents ($7,929,596.45)
21 or so much thereof as may be necessary to address the ongoing
22 increased demand for mental health services by expanding the
23 infrastructure of the Tulsa Center for Behavioral Health to increase
24 capacity. Such funds shall be utilized in a manner consistent with
